short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: One click to export like user list of any x/twitter tweets to CSV.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Scrape and Extract X/Twitter Like user list of any tweet, Save Twitter like list to CSV / Excel / JSON.
Automatic handling of rate limit errors.

HOW TO USE?
1. Enter a Tweet link
2. Click the start button

🔥 Upgrade
✔︎ Support X.com and Twitter.com tweet links.
✔︎ Add websites, first name and last name fields. You can find emails with domain and name by some email hunters.

👋 FAQ
https://twlikesexport.extensionsfox.com/#faq
If you have any questions, please keep in touch via help@extensionsfox.com.

👐 X/TWITTER TOOL FAMILY
you can visit other X/twitter tools on the tools menu.
✔︎ TwDM - Send bulk DMs to target users
✔︎ TwScrape - Export followers and following
✔︎ TwSearch - Extract search result to CSV
✔︎ TwReplyExport - Export tweet replies

🔒 DATA PRIVACY
All data is processed in your local computer, never passing through our web server, and no one knows what you save.
